  "text": "Like the retractions, we define δ ↑ again by utilizing the methodology of fuzzy control. Recall that the fuzzification of FLS introduced in the previous section can merely cope with crisp inputs. In order to handle fuzzy inputs, we have to seek other fuzzification techniques. In [CITATION_1] , Foulloy and Galichet provided a means of introducing fuzzy inputs in Takagi-Sugeno-Kang type FLS. In a similar manner, we can develop a fuzzification for dealing with fuzzy inputs in our context.",
